<main>
    <h2>Save The Reef</h2>

    <div class="introduction">
        <p>The oceans are dying at an alarming rate. Yada yada. Beautiful world. Let's do this and bring back the color to the reef.
<br>
<br>
            If we want our kids to see what we have been able to see for all these years let's join forces and bring back the color!
        </p>
    </div>

    <form id="login" name="login" method="POST">
        <div class="warning"><h3>{{incorrect}}</div>
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
        <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email" required autofocus>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
        <input id="submit" type="submit" value="Login">
    </form>
</main>
